name: Tsunade Senju
description:
It is a character LoRA of Tsunade Senju from Naruto. V1.0 was trained on AbyssOrangeMix2_hard model. V1.1 was trained on NovelAI.

For better appearance add "mature, blonde hair, blue forehead mark, simple kimono, green jacket"

modelVersions.name: v1.1
modelVersions.description: Retrained the model with larger dataset on NovelAI model following this guide: https://civitai.com/models/22530/guide-make-your-own-loras-easy-and-free
